B.PJ=new A.S(B.B,"\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Cabin Safety Equipment","**Portable oxygen unit** \u2014 portable O\u2082 bottle for crew use\n**Drop-down oxygen mask** \u2014 passenger masks, auto-deploys above 10,000 ft cabin alt\n**Life vest / Life jacket** \u2014 under-seat flotation device\n**Emergency exit** \u2014 floor-level lighting marks the path\n**Escape slide** \u2014 inflatable slide for rapid evacuation\n**Fire extinguisher** \u2014 Halon type in cockpit, water/CO\u2082 in cabin\n**ELT** \u2014 Emergency Locator Transmitter (activates on impact)",null,null,null)
B.PU=new A.S(B.B,"\ud83d\udd27 Technical Safety Equipment","**Circuit breaker (CB)** \u2014 protects electrical circuits from overload\n**Fire detector** \u2014 senses smoke/heat in engine, APU, cargo compartment\n**Fire suppression system** \u2014 discharges extinguisher agent into engine nacelle\n**Overheat detector** \u2014 warns of bleed air duct overheating\n**TCAS** \u2014 Traffic Collision Avoidance System\n**GPWS/EGPWS** \u2014 Ground Proximity Warning System",null,null,null)
B.Jb=new A.aB("Oxygen masks will drop down automatically if cabin altitude exceeds 10,000 feet.","Kabin irtifas\u0131 10.000 fiti a\u015farsa oksijen maskeleri otomatik olarak d\xfc\u015fer.","drop down automatically")
B.K3=new A.aB("The fire suppression system discharged successfully into the engine nacelle.","Yang\u0131n bast\u0131rma sistemi motor kovan\u0131na ba\u015far\u0131yla de\u015farj edildi.","fire suppression system")
B.Ji=new A.aB("All cabin crew must demonstrate the life vest donning procedure to passengers.","T\xfcm kabin ekibi yolculara can yele\u011fi giyinme prosed\xfcr\xfcn\xfc g\xf6stermelidir.","donning procedure")
